{"tid":680378,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔怪派膠卡利奧斯　神軒︰皇馬值得贏","createTime":"2018-05-27T06:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T07:55:38.000Z","uid":5006,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"257f77b379599623300db3bf19a4b736ad85a02d","tid":680378,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180527/large/1527399874_e5dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180527%2Flarge%2F1527399874_e5dc.jpg&h=eb1e5ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦周六在歐聯決賽以1:3不敵皇家馬德里，隊長佐敦軒達臣賽後表示不會怪責在比賽中兩度「派膠」的門將卡利奧斯，並指皇馬奪取歐聯三連冠是值得的。<br />\n<br />\n卡利奧斯首次失誤被賓施馬為皇馬先開紀錄，不過在沙迪奧文尼為紅軍扳平1:1後，加里夫巴利先後倒掛入球及遠射破網，而後一球則是卡利奧斯擋入己隊網窩。<br />\n<br />\n然而，「神軒」賽後說︰「當然這是失望的。我們以好表現追回一球，但我們犯了錯，而皇馬實在很出色。他們是一支非常棒的球隊，總是令你受傷，他們是值得勝出的，今晚他們是表現較佳的一隊。」他又謂紅軍在首30或35分鐘佔優勢，並且有一定機會，輸球是失望但亦要讚揚皇馬。<br />\n<br />\n利記在下半場因為卡秉奧斯失誤而被賓施馬射入今場決賽的第一球，軒達臣說︰「<span style=\"color: red;\">那第一球我不肯定發生甚麼事</span>&hellip;&hellip;然後那倒掛入球，他（卡利奧斯）是無能為力的。第三個入球，那球負載很大的動力，不是卡利奧斯犯的錯，我們以一個團隊殺入決賽，輸球亦是一個團隊，是關乎所有人的。」「今晚我們不夠，我為球員和支持我們的球迷感自豪，希望我們可以繼續打入更多決賽，並以此繼續前進。」<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180527/58243473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F58243473&d=0gAxxgObGgPCwDOQEb4rKosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=0048a976\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F58243473&h=d4ff0bd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180527/58243473</a><br />\n<br />\n屌，神軒睇撚左第一球playback先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都以為佢接左個波會開返出去 <br />\n轉頭就入左都唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"9b09916ab09839593d3a1e779872a506dc0d35a0","tid":680378,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"總是令你受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c398f73928543397ef4cc8f6473d875394f1789","tid":680378,"uid":5191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"屌 死利狗又唔撐隊友"},{"pid":"5fe558aafbf933354b2a7495bcd6150e2375222d","tid":680378,"uid":38189,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"神軒有風度過波台98.2729%利迷"},{"pid":"8056d1438265f881d070668ac158a25ac0fc3a56","tid":680378,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"一定係扮野"},{"pid":"5f0cc77f6832040b7633248d9b07c117b1e758bd","tid":680378,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe558aafbf933354b2a7495bcd6150e2375222d","tid":680378,"uid":38189,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"神軒有風度過波台98.2729%利迷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"迷軒了"},{"pid":"534f413d2c43dbaf2878c779d3f6f3cb46adc504","tid":680378,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"呢d公關野，點會講真話<br />\n唔通公開屌自己隊友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01855ed950b37c41cca5d403060b51034218444","tid":680378,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"風度軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d93b6fc35471c901717a1e7b089a90069845466","tid":680378,"uid":171177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38ac3d815a0032b6291b2ac15103f42b9a08e167","tid":680378,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"神軒真隊長<img src=\"/asset